    - Fix reports/list missing ownership filter for non-admin users
    - Add ownership checks to report export endpoints (JSON/CSV/PDF)
    - Add ownership check to GET /api/scan/:id for non-admin users
    - Add ownership check to scan compare endpoint
    - Add ownership checks to CBOM record/list endpoints
    - Enforce password policy in admin user creation
    - Fix CbomRecord status enum missing 'error' value
    - Add DB connection retry logic (5 retries, 3s delay)
    - Replace inaccurate getNextRun() with proper cron forward-search parser
    - Add pagination to GET /api/scan (page/limit query params)
    - Fix test-register.js to use password meeting the policy
    - Update client to handle paginated scan response
    - Add 17-test unit test suite with npm test script
    
    Co-authored-by: varunsanjeevula <222699877+varunsanjeevula@users.noreply.github.com>

